Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太这个大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.46,0:04:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来冬海同学的可爱万人迷程度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.47,0:04:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是完全敌不过锐太的迟钝程度呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.36,0:04:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来那你的可爱万人迷程度又怎样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.66,0:04:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.65,0:04:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就是动物园里的考拉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说谁是「小熊饼」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}注：指「乐天小熊饼」的考拉图案设计
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.15,0:04:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪有说  难道你还是巧克力夹心的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做这种恋爱头脑才会做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你意图何在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了向别人显示我们的「男女朋友」关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.85,0:05:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  那三个人完全没有看过来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.49,0:05:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都玩得正欢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.61,0:05:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(340,52)\fn@方正准圆_GBK\frz-90\fs16\3c9D86D0}弹珠汽水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.42,0:05:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思议的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过味道本身只是一般般
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调味酱也只有咸味而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.08,0:05:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全说不上美味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面糊了这一点最致命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不可思议的是让人吃起来欲罢不能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  难得说了中二以外的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.60,0:05:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在海边吃什么都美味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.39,0:05:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道偏重难道是考虑到了那些刚游完泳很累的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.56,0:06:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锐太同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.16,0:06:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你准备一下甜点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.39,0:06:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.99,0:06:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  锐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.36,0:06:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要劈得像可爱万人迷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锐太要使出可爱万人迷流剑术  完全不在话下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为可爱万人迷风纪委员  就让我来给你劈西瓜打个分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.26,0:06:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么可爱万人迷  可爱万人迷的  吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  棍子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请动用脑袋来劈西瓜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.35,0:06:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是让我用智慧来解决吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.88,0:06:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  是让你用额头狠命砸下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.25,0:06:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是物理性的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啊  来啊  锐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这边  在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.68,0:06:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锐太  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边是冥界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.42,0:06:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.77,0:06:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,季堂同学  是这边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听从风纪委员的话一定没错的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.32,0:06:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  锐太同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.87,0:06:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在混淆视听
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确的只有我这个女朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有夏川的话不能相信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.99,0:07:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会长是暗黑邪神  混沌魔王  恶魔将军
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.89,0:07:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心啊  这个女人可是会让季堂同学堕落的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信我的「女友」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(180,350)\fs22}不要过去  锐太
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,350)\fs22}说什么傻话  等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}不行啊  锐  真的不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.48,0:07:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真凉  西瓜在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.11,0:07:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝这边直走3米
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.57,0:07:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请飞扑过来拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.70,0:07:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,350)\fs22}给我等一下啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}锐  不是那边  是这里啊  锐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(180,350)\fs22}…那边是怒之黑暗  回来  快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.91,0:07:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西瓜到手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上最柔软的  纯白的西瓜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.75,0:07:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  锐太同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.95,0:07:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西瓜好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.06,0:07:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞什么鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都不来抱紧我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.20,0:08:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要脸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.47,0:08:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(280,130)\fn@方正粗圆_GBK\frz-90\fs18\1c807977\bord0}不要脸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.70,0:08:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  被镌刻的罪之烙印吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.74,0:08:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有面糊了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.96,0:08:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去买吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.37,0:08:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  请锐太同学更换一下吊灯的灯泡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.58,0:08:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯丝好像断了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.38,0:08:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.45,0:08:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  夏川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和季堂同学交往之后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.03,0:08:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就没再被别人表白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.79,0:08:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:08:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有看到过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.56,0:09:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在体育馆后面被表白后叹气的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男生真是气势汹汹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很讨厌那种被拒之后就反过来发怒的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.87,0:09:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老碰上那样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.44,0:09:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确会让人开始讨厌被表白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.31,0:09:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想干脆随便找个人交往也完全可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.94,0:09:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  如果是以此为目的才和季堂同学交往
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.72,0:09:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能无法原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相到底是怎样的  夏川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬海同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.53,0:09:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋葱要剥到什么程度才算好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.47,0:09:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要剥到最里面去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.18,0:09:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要剥掉褐色的那层皮就够了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.02,0:09:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  难怪剥起来没个底了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.00,0:10:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在变成这样之前不问问我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再碰蔬菜了  给我去淘米吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.81,0:10:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  别用洗洁精啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会在淘米的时候用洗洁精啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.43,0:10:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为你死认真办坏事我才这么说的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.49,0:10:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然说出那种话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要不做蠢事  我也不会那样想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要决定性的证据呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.90,0:10:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  听不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.35,0:10:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要给她们看看决定性的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.81,0:10:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正在交往的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:10:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那种东西  就算你突然这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:10:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…要怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送礼物之类的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.35,0:11:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用实物可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要更有冲击性
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.19,0:11:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要那种她们一看就会相信的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.69,0:11:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲击性…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.74,0:11:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈风斩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.66,0:11:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用烈风斩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.99,0:11:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.71,0:11:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈风斩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.62,0:11:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说接吻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.04,0:11:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在众目睽睽之下装作若无其事的样子比较好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是日常功课一般
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.96,0:11:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是很自然地打个招呼一般
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.82,0:11:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你来吻我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.93,0:11:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.97,0:11:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  为什么这么吃惊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是已经吻过好多次了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.45,0:11:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区接吻  对我们这种反对恋爱的人来说并没有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但对她们这些恋爱头脑来说可是很有冲击性的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.05,0:11:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道这会让事态发展成什么样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.88,0:11:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  会变成修罗场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说得这么事不关己  这可是三人份啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.07,0:11:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  正如你所说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.20,0:12:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说这次我就给你一个「选择权」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.44,0:12:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.50,0:12:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会拿笔记本的秘密当盾牌来强迫你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.28,0:12:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是选择接吻还是选择不接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.33,0:12:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你来决定  季堂锐太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.59,0:12:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.63,0:12:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锐你好弱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红桃三是这张哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.35,0:12:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你不擅长记东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.63,0:12:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是  啊哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.73,0:12:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计划如下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在和大家度过愉快的时间以后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.44,0:12:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先说着「我累了  先去休息」站起身来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.48,0:12:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随后我会说「晚安  亲爱的」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.72,0:13:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就在我耳边轻声说一句「啊  晚安  甜心」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.58,0:13:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后顺势吻我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.94,0:13:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当是欧美情侣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.50,0:13:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锐？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.79,0:13:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.04,0:13:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  没有那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很精神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家呢  还行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.36,0:13:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我倒是没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.89,0:13:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}啊  没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果吻了真凉  就是直奔修罗场路线了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.41,0:13:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}话说刚才的邮件是发给米歇尔的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过如果不吻她而选择趋近后宫路线
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}是噢  如果不每天发邮件的话  他会寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.17,0:13:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}米歇尔怕寂寞？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.63,0:13:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}是噢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.35,0:13:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒牌关系暴露也就只是时间问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.36,0:13:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.15,0:13:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我觉得有点累  先去休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.66,0:13:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  说出口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.98,0:13:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那今天就到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.74,0:13:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么啊  你不用配合我结束啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.76,0:13:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦  反正也玩腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个  今天我有东西想交给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.86,0:14:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.05,0:14:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个给锐  这个给夏川
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.34,0:14:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.63,0:14:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五个人都一样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.93,0:14:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是姬儿负责设计的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.29,0:14:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便说一句  那可不是字母「Z」而是「乙女」的「乙」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.29,0:14:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}注：日语中少女写作「乙女」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.94,0:14:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大师找到了能给我们制作的店家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.45,0:14:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提议的是千和哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.78,0:14:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想  体育社团大都会有统一的制服之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是咱们社团没有那种东西呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.01,0:14:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得好不容易成为正式社团了  这样实在有点寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.76,0:14:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就和她们俩商量了看看可以做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.98,0:14:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事对夏川同学保密了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.11,0:14:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟你是建立这个社团的功臣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.57,0:14:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就当是社员送给你的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么连我都保密啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.89,0:15:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是告诉锐  不就泄露给夏川了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.94,0:15:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你撒谎能力超级差的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.57,0:15:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就是选美大赛了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.33,0:15:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决出胜负之后再送也不太方便
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.56,0:15:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想趁现在送啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.56,0:15:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来千和她们之所以互相联络
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.21,0:15:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是为了搅和我们的关系  而是为了这件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,败给你们了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.93,0:15:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们送我这个饱含心意的吊饰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.08,0:15:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会好好珍惜的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.75,0:15:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.18,0:15:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那种情况下我没办法吻你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.13,0:15:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候你要是强吻的话  我一定会鄙视你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.86,0:15:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不由得感动了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也重新认识到自己是多么丑陋的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.48,0:16:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这只是碰巧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.54,0:16:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是碰巧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.82,0:16:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春咲同学她们在敌视我的同时  还能够送礼物给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.16,0:16:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够为敌视的对手送上这样的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们就是这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.39,0:16:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我实在是差太远了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.47,0:16:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的选美大赛  拿不了第一了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.74,0:16:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.66,0:16:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆弃权吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我也想过  但考虑到她们的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.49,0:16:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是应该如期现身参赛  然后接受审判吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被我抢走以后  春咲同学有多么懊悔  多么伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.93,0:16:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考虑到这点  我就无法不战而败
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\an7\pos(70,10)\fn@方正准圆_GBK\frz-90\fs20\1c926F74\bord0}九月十日  晴\N我要成为医生\N治好千和的身体!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你陪我到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.98,0:17:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次合宿结束以后  你就自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.37,0:17:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会长还是没起床
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明昨天还很有精神的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她还能参加选美吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几点开始来着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.11,0:17:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,16点进场  16点半开演呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.59,0:17:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参赛者要在15点半之前在特设舞台前集合哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前  她应该…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.19,0:17:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们先去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.83,0:17:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待会儿一定要来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.78,0:17:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.72,0:18:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真凉  你还在睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饿了吧  要不要吃点挂面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  现在能让我一个人待会儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.07,0:18:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒辣的太阳  in the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.28,0:18:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心也  in the blu…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.40,0:18:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}躲开  躲开  躲开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.09,0:18:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.81,0:18:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.34,0:19:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碰我啊  痴汉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.55,0:19:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶心宅男  恶心处男
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  处男吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.01,0:19:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说这是最棒的夸奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.40,0:19:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.06,0:19:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.94,0:19:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶心  恶心  恶心  恶心  恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死  去死  去死  去死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.83,0:19:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处男去死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样  再来几句
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  难得的胜地度假全毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.70,0:19:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有钱人就该去国外啊  国外
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.69,0:19:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种地方早就去过了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.43,0:19:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且这里也不是你这种人该待的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.74,0:19:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真烦人  我是来合宿的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.18,0:19:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小凉也来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.98,0:19:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.25,0:19:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凉怎么样了啊  身体好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好好吃饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.21,0:19:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很在意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.63,0:19:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是在意  其实我只是有义务向爸爸汇报而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.62,0:19:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说你还是很喜欢真凉的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.17,0:20:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴  处男
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.45,0:20:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  发生了这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.63,0:20:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凉她一直被称作「夏川家的宝石」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.29,0:20:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝石  也就是「装饰品」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.51,0:20:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爸爸在交际界用来炫耀的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.09,0:20:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把小凉和她母亲拆散  带到自己身边也正是为了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.38,0:20:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凉的举手投足正如父亲期待的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美地演绎了一个聪明端庄  又尊敬父亲的温顺女儿形象
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我这样的  爸爸完全不抱期待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.79,0:20:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是小凉她却能做到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.15,0:20:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  她就努力扮演爸爸所期待的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.06,0:20:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后变成了怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.22,0:20:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凉不断欺骗着自己  结果渐渐失去了真实的自我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.00,0:21:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凉说的话都相当荒谬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.82,0:21:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才刚说完非常苛刻的话  下一秒又变温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.67,0:21:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后又变得冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.52,0:21:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也被折腾得够呛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.51,0:21:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.07,0:21:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都被她折腾着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.72,0:21:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这也并不坏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.61,0:21:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的日子并不坏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.36,0:21:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.87,0:21:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你能喜欢上我的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.84,0:21:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  如果有能和真凉在一起的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.18,0:21:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得那会是什么样的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.00,0:21:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和骗子在一起的  那还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.13,0:21:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮凶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.47,0:22:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.33,0:22:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我娇小姐选美大赛现在开始咯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.76,0:23:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集的可爱万人迷道具是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.09,0:23:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,率真的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.27,0:23:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有再多的话语交流
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.35,0:23:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果内容空洞无物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.92,0:23:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算再怎么率真
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.65,0:23:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是毫无意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.07,0:23:39.91,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fnArial}# 13{\r}  走向新世界的修罗场
